The system started at 13:12:15 and at 20:24:46 was on agent #710. That's 7h12m for 710 agents.

Key observations:
1. **Each call takes 60-134s** - this is the kiro-cli subprocess overhead + LLM time + MCP tool calls
2. **Depth explosion is real**: Within the first 10 minutes, 4 child contentions were spawned from 4 parent contentions (all at round 1!)
